feedback: This is one of the greatest taxi services that I have ever used. Would higly recommend the L type taxi. It is the best when compared to other services.
This was a lifesaver to me, there was one time I was in a rush, just tweeted to ALTA to request a taxi, and it took only about 5 minutes.

There is not much trouble using these services. Just tweeted to ALTA and the employees are fast to respond.
                            Although, the cars are not exceptional.
Kahn was a fantastic driver, very chatty and friendly!
Didn’t like the service, it was very slow and the customer service is terrible.
Good friend Khan – simply excellent driver
Great ride, but it was rather cold in the car
